creator: DeliverLogic
descriptionHtml:
Drive, Deliver, Satisfy
This app enables delivery drivers to receive orders and earn money for
executing the delivery of those orders.

Who are we?
The DeliverLogic Network includes over 100 Delivery Service Partners, and 40,000
restaurants in 43 states and 12 countries. Find more information at
https://www.deliverlogic.com/drivers/.
descriptionShort: Enables delivery drivers to receive orders and earn money.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fix issues with dispatcher checking a driver in
Fix issue with signature pad not showing in certain conditions

title: Driver Logic

creator: DeliverLogic
descriptionHtml:
Drive. Deliver. Satisfy. Get Paid.

If you are a Delivery Service Provider, Fleet Manager, or Independent Driver, DriverLogic enables you to easily manage and execute real-time delivery orders and make great money while doing so.

The DriverLogic App optimizes delivering restaurant food orders that are placed through Restaurant Delivery Services or directly on restaurant websites and apps around the world.

Drivers: Easily capture orders, use your favorite navigation app to execute your food delivery, and get paid.

Delivery Service Providers: Hire, manage, and monetize your own delivery service business. Utilize DriverLogic with the DeliverLogic software system to AUTOMATE your own delivery service business with ease.

The DeliverLogic Network includes over:
-100 Delivery Service Partners
-30,000 Drivers
-40,000 Restaurants
-43 States
-12 Countries

Find more information at https://www.deliverlogic.com.
descriptionShort: Enables delivery drivers to receive orders and earn money.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Brand New Release
New Framework (slicker, faster, better, smoother)
Our newest release is built on a brand new platform. There are over 50 upgrades.
Drivers see exactly how much they will make from a preview screen, they are notified on how much they have made during their day.
Easily call and text customers.
Take Photos of orders to verify drop off or verify identity.
All and all, the app is much better and we look forward to any feedback.
